<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الدَّرْكِ}</span> ... المَنْزِلَةِ، وَالطَّبَقِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الطُّورَ}</span> ... جَبَلًا بِسَيْنَاءَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا تَعْدُوا}</span> ... لَا تَعْتَدُوا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غُلْفٌ}</span> ... مُغَطَّاةٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرَّاسِخُونَ}</span> ... المُتَمَكِّنُونَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالأَسْبَاطِ}</span> ... الأَنْبِيَاءِ مِنْ وَلَدِ يَعْقُوبَ - عليه السلام -، الَّذِينَ بُعِثُوا فِي قَبَائِلِ بَنِي إِسْرَائِيلَ الاِثْنَتَيْ عَشْرَةَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا تَغْلُوا}</span> ... لَا تَتَجَاوَزُوا الاِعْتِقَادَ الْحَقَّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَكَلِمَتُهُ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> خَلَقَهُ بِالْكَلِمَةِ الَّتِي أَرْسَلَ بِهَا جِبْرِيلَ إِلَى مَرْيَمَ وَهِيَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كُنْ»</span>؛ فَكَانَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَسْتَنكِفَ}</span> ... يَانَفَ، وَيَمْتَنِعَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُرْهَانٌ}</span> ... دَلِيلٌ صَادِقٌ، وَهُوَ مُحَمَّدٌ - صلى الله عليه وسلم -.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْكَلَالَةِ}</span> ... مَنْ مَاتَ وَلَيْسَ لَهُ وَلَدٌ، وَلَا وَالِدٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَهُ أُخْتٌ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> أُخْتٌ شَقِيقَةٌ، أَوْ لِأَبٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>